---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'Internal Sprint 01 — Signal Capture';
---

<BaseLayout title={title}>
  <section class="runbook">
    <h1>Internal Sprint 01 — Signal Capture</h1>

    <p class="subtitle">
      Capture deterministic, evidence-backed signals from a framework execution environment.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h2>🎯 Objective</h2>
    <p>
      Establish a reliable signal layer by executing validation commands and capturing
      their raw outputs without interpretation.
    </p>

    <h2>🧩 System Flow</h2>
    <pre>
Framework Under Test
        ↓
Validation Commands
        ↓
Raw Logs + Runtime Signals
        ↓
validation-output/
    </pre>

    <h2>📦 Inputs</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Framework repository (Playwright, Cypress, etc.)</li>
      <li>Validation command definitions</li>
      <li>Execution environment (local or CI)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>⚙️ Execution</h2>
    <pre>
node agents/run-assessment-agents.js out/current-playwright-framework-input.json
    </pre>

    <h2>📤 Outputs</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>validation-output/run_all_validation_commands.log</code></li>
      <li><code>out/framework-assessment.json</code></li>
      <li><code>out/framework-assessment-wrapper.json</code></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>📏 Acceptance Criteria</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>All validation commands execute without silent failure</li>
      <li>Log file is non-empty</li>
      <li>Signals include timestamps and command context</li>
      <li>No inferred or derived values at this stage</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>⚠️ Failure Modes</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Empty log file (no signal captured)</li>
      <li>Partial execution (commands skipped)</li>
      <li>Runtime crash without log output</li>
      <li>Environment misconfiguration (missing BASE_URL, etc.)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>🧠 Principles</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Capture first, interpret later</li>
      <li>All signals must be reproducible</li>
      <li>No transformation at this stage</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>🧪 Verification</h2>
    <pre>
wc -l validation-output/run_all_validation_commands.log
cat validation-output/run_all_validation_commands.log | head
    </pre>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.runbook { max-width: 900px; margin: auto; }
.subtitle { color: #cbd5e1; }
pre { background: #111827; padding: 16px; border-radius: 6px; }
</style>